<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM4.6.4">
<l>muṉaimukat tarakkaṉ māḷa muṭikaḷpat taṟuttu vīḻttāṅ</l>
<l>kaṉaiyavaṟ kiḷaiya vaṟkē yaracaḷit taruḷi ṉāṉē</l>
<l>cuṉaikaḷil kayalkaḷ pāyac curumputēṉ nukarum nāṅkaik</l>
<l>kaṉaikaḻal kāva ḷantaṇ pāṭiyāy kaḷaika ṇīyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>[You] who were gracious, having cut and fell the ten crowns of the demon</l>
<l>So that he died there at the battlefront, bestowing the kingdom</l>
<l rend="indent">to the one who was younger than that one,</l>
<l>You with rattling war anklets in the cool hamlet of Kāvaḷam in Nāṅkai</l>
<l>Where bees sip nectar while kayal [fish] leap in pools,</l>
<l rend="indent">only you are [our] refuge.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
